<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_bee11a2f-3c39-4bba-8495-74660b13a17a" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="SA"><sptc>I4D8</sptc><title id="_4e9c1fc1-e804-4b95-9295-a550af546313">Smoke venting</title><subclause id="_d657c4f6-d296-43b3-bacd-d66a210cbac1" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_e3a93f74-6137-46a2-97fb-50aa356ac7e0">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>In a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/2466_1.0.0.xml#_0ea6e30e-b7ce-4b3d-ab37-7888621a4eac" id="_0cacc2e2-e5ef-4549-8cee-9eed299bf5ba" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">bulk grain storage facility</xref>, suitable natural smoke venting by fixed vents must be provided at the top of elevator towers and overhead galleries in a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/2468_0.7.0.xml#_77fc5383-ae28-4bfd-ad12-0d5735cf1366" id="_826f4223-1a97-4869-bfb1-67f37958118b" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">cell type silo</xref>.</p></subclause><subclause id="_f429034a-03a9-404d-806f-a691f94fa247" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_34a81884-bb9f-4355-8524-9cfb06795f58">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>Smoke venting is not required in a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/2474_25.0.0.xml#_638ea3e1-f483-40cc-9e79-5291637c5f3e" id="_91bc5534-29fc-42f6-a189-34effce52f8f" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">storage shed</xref> of a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/2466_1.0.0.xml#_0ea6e30e-b7ce-4b3d-ab37-7888621a4eac" id="_0597bb19-fd42-4d41-acd5-d7bb7533f104" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">bulk grain storage facility</xref>.</p></subclause></clause>